OL,3,CNorris and Piastri ruled out of
OL,4,CChinese Grand prix by mechanical
OL,5,Cfailure
OL,7,FFormula 1 champion Lando Norris and
OL,8,Fhis McLaren teammate Oscar Piastri
OL,9,Fwere both unable to start the Chinese
OL,10,FGrand Prix after hitting technical
OL,11,Fproblems minutes before the race began.
OL,13,FPiastri was due to start fifth and
OL,14,FNorris sixth for Sunday's race. Norris
OL,15,Fwas in his car in the pits but didn't
OL,16,Fleave for the grid before Piastri was
OL,17,Fthen withdrawn from the grid following
OL,18,Fa radio message which indicated an
OL,19,Felectrical issue.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
