OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773659109
OL,3,CNorris and Piastri ruled out of
OL,4,CChinese Grand prix by mechanical
OL,5,Cfailure
OL,7,F"Unfortunately, we identified separate
OL,8,Fissues on both cars, which prevented
OL,9,Fthem from starting the Chinese GP,
OL,10,Fwith Oscar's being removed from the
OL,11,Fgrid shortly before the formation lap.
OL,12,FWe will now work to identify each
OL,13,Fissue," McLaren said.
OL,15,FIt's the second time Piastri has
OL,16,Ffailed to start in 2026 after he
OL,17,Fcrashed before the start of last
OL,18,Fweek's race in Australia.
