OL,3,CNorris and Piastri ruled out of
OL,4,CChinese Grand prix by mechanical
OL,5,Cfailure
OL,7,FKimi Antonelli was seeking to convert
OL,8,Fhis record-breaking pole position into
OL,9,Fa first career win, but will have to
OL,10,Fstay ahead of his Mercedes teammate
OL,11,FGeorge Russell.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
