OL,3,CNorris and Piastri ruled out of
OL,4,CChinese Grand prix by mechanical
OL,5,Cfailure
OL,7,FAntonelli became the youngest driver
OL,8,Fto qualify on pole position for an F1
OL,9,FGrand Prix race on Saturday. The 19-
OL,10,Fyear-old Italian starts on the front
OL,11,Frow alongside Russell, who recovered
OL,12,Ffrom technical problems to post the
OL,13,Fsecond-fastest time.
OL,15,FThey're looking to continue Mercedes
OL,16,Fdominance in F1's new era of
OL,17,Fregulations after Russell won last
OL,18,Fweek's Australian Grand Prix and the
OL,19,Fsprint race in China on Saturday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
