OL,3,CNorris and Piastri ruled out of
OL,4,CChinese Grand prix by mechanical
OL,5,Cfailure
OL,7,FLewis Hamilton of Ferrari briefly got
OL,8,Fahead of Antonelli at the start, but
OL,9,Fthe Italian took the place back soon
OL,10,Fafter.
OL,12,FF1 is racing hours after it announced
OL,13,Fnext month's races in Bahrain and
OL,14,FSaudi Arabia will not go ahead because
OL,15,Fof the war in the Middle East.
